FT  06 JAN 93 / Observer: Over the hill
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
When a troubled construction company makes its personnel director redundant,
one might well think that the only people left on the premises are the
bailiffs.
But Higgs &amp; Hill stresses that Stephen Schneider, who has resigned as a
